Hello, I received an email from Clickbank today saying we could get $500 for our campaign? I am wondering how I would go about doing that?

Hi Melinda, it sounds like you're referring to a cashback or bonus offer. For ClickBank campaigns, NewsBreak offers cashbacks based on the amount you spend. For example, for $100k spent, you get 2%, for $250k spent, you get 2.5%, and for $500k spent, you get 3%. If you need more details on how to set up your ClickBank Postback on NewsBreak, you can check out this guide: [How to set up a ClickBank Postback on NewsBreak](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/23746617571341-How-to-set-up-a-ClickBank-Postback-on-NewsBreak). Let me know if you have any other questions!
